snippet.title: Geometry - Inscribed Angles
snippet.description:
The MathemaGYPTIAN is back with a video on inscribed angles in circles. The lesson begins and ends with a free-style rap, and in between we solve four circles for their inscribed angles. Great interaction and learning today, YAY MATH!

Learning should always be fun and connective. Please visit http://www.yaymath.org for:
• all videos
• free quizzes
• free worksheets
• debut book on how to connect with and inspire students
• all-in-one math courses that teachers and parents can use, backed by Yay Math energy
